Weapon Engraving: Air.description:
Engrave an air rune onto your weapon for 1 hour.

Grants your direct damage dealt a 15% chance to replicate 30% of the damage dealt to the target.

@ext:Can only have 1 type of |cffffffffWeapon Engraving|r active at a time.:ext@

Weapon Engraving: Arcane.description:
Engrave an arcane rune onto your weapon for 1 hour.

Grants your direct damage dealt a 25% chance to deal 54 Arcane damage to the target and reduce their healing received by 30% for 10 sec.

@ext:Can only have 1 type of |cffffffffWeapon Engraving|r active at a time.:ext@

Weapon Engraving: Earth.description:
Engrave an earth rune onto your weapon for 1 hour.

Grants your direct damage dealt a 15% chance to deal an additional 1 Nature damage to enemies within 5 yds of your target.

@ext:Can only have 1 type of |cffffffffWeapon Engraving|r active at a time.:ext@

Weapon Engraving: Ice.description:
Engrave an ice rune onto your weapon for 1 hour.

Grants your direct damage dealt a 40% chance to deal 5 Frost damage and slow the target's movement speed by 1 to 0% for until cancelled.

@ext:Can only have 1 type of |cffffffffWeapon Engraving|r active at a time.:ext@

Weapon Engraving: Water.description:
Engrave a water rune onto your weapon for 1 hour.

Grants your direct damage dealt a 30% chance to deal 1 Frost damage, drain 1 mana from the target, and grant allies |cffffffffReplenishment|r.@s:560582:0@

@ext:Can only have 1 type of |cffffffffWeapon Engraving|r active at a time.:ext@
